# 3DFlatter agent pointer

- Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) at session start for commands, boundaries, and architecture.
- Follow [docs/decisions/0001-mesh-model-and-topology.md](docs/decisions/0001-mesh-model-and-topology.md) for mesh, seam, and topology contracts.
- Prefer minimal diffs; extend existing code in `src/logic/`; ask before architectural changes or new dependencies.
- Run `npm test` before marking work complete.
